Package: tomio.signals
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-06-01 - 2026
Title: Easy signal processing tools for R
Author: Tamás Haraszti [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Tamás Haraszti <haraszti@dwi.rwth-aachen.de>
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Suggests:
Description: Signal processing has several tasks. This small library focuses on using a Gaussian kernel to smooth data or differeitiate with smoothing. A non-zero padding FFT based convolution filter is provided for this purpose. Another function uses the first derivative for an easy peak detector.
